	(45,2,'2014-07-29 06:24:58','2014-07-29 06:24:58','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco depends on the generosity of our volunteer community to provide time, talent and all types of support.  “In-kind” donations, contributions of materials, goods and services, allow us to provide for families in a “home away from home” environment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>We are always seeking a variety of new and unused household goods such as:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Paper towels</li>\r\n	<li>Arm and Hammer Dermatologist tested No Scent Laundry Detergent</li>\r\n	<li>Ajax Grapefruit Dish Soap</li>\r\n	<li>Cascade Complete</li>\r\n	<li>Shampoo</li>\r\n	<li>Conditioner</li>\r\n	<li>Body Wash (dermatologist tested/non allergenic)</li>\r\n	<li>Lysol Disinfecting Wipes Ocean Fresh Scent (80 wipes we utilize in 1 week)</li>\r\n	<li>Simple Green Pro 3</li>\r\n	<li>Scrubbing Bubbles</li>\r\n	<li>Windex</li>\r\n	<li>Individual snacks (chips, cookies, fruit snacks, granola bars, pudding)</li>\r\n	<li>White bath &amp; hand towels &amp; washcloths</li>\r\n	<li>Queen size white sheets &amp; pillowcases</li>\r\n	<li>Drawstring garbage bags (kitchen &amp; 33-gallon)</li>\r\n	<li>Gift cards such as Target, Smart &amp; Final, Safeway, Costco, Chevron, Subway</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Please visit our Amazon wishlist for our current needs:</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><a style=\"color: #800000;\" title=\"Holiday Wish List\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/registry/wishlist/3ABUAKBDIV4M1/ref=topnav_lists_1\" target=\"_blank\">2014 Holiday Wishlist!</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><a style=\"color: #800000;\" title=\"Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco Wishlist\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/registry/wishlist/101NPRNN8CD93/ref=cm_sw_su_w\" target=\"_blank\">Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco Wishlist</a></span>\r\n\r\n<em>Any questions, suggestions or concerns please contact </em><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><a style=\"color: #800000;\" href=\"mailto:Melinda@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">melinda@ronaldhouse-sf.org</a></span>.\r\n\r\nItems can be dropped off at the House at 1640 Scott Street, San Francisco, CA 94115.\r\nTo arrange a drop-off date and time please call us at (415) 673-0891.\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">Thank you for your support!</h2>\r\n</div>','Our Wish List','','publish','open','closed','','wish-list','','','2014-11-24 17:18:40','2014-11-25 01:18:40','',33,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com?page_id=45',3,'page','',0),
