	(388,4,'2014-12-11 11:01:35','2014-12-11 19:01:35','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Join us in fulfilling our mission! We have an array of important positions, for both individuals and groups. Volunteers are strong partners in the work we do. We welcome corporate teams, office groups, schools, service organizations, alumni groups, associations, families, fraternities, sororities and religious organizations. You are an essential part of making our house a home.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">We understand that helpful hearts have busy calendars. Therefore, we have redesigned our volunteer program to work within your schedule.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Join us for a Volunteer Informational session held every Wednesday at 6:00pm. **Attending a Volunteer Informational Session does not guarantee volunteer placement. Please complete the application below to register.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Current Volunteer Opportunities</strong></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/scott.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-394\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/scott-300x228.png\" alt=\"scott\" width=\"233\" height=\"177\" /></a>      <a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Mission.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-395\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Mission-300x205.png\" alt=\"Mission\" width=\"244\" height=\"167\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>  Volunteer at the Scott Street House              Volunteer at the Mission Bay House</strong></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/cbp.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-396\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07